column5: Hey Guys,  I pulled this 3 minute clip from a largie shoot we did last season - Who can guess where we were fishing?!? Hope you enjoy!  Cheers, Ryan  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6ZHlV9YinVw&feature=player_embedded
I PVR every episode from WFN and Sportsnet HD. That's 3 episodes each day lol Seen every one at least 3 times.
lol then this is old new for you!    Some of the boys and gals here don't have WFN or The Score so I've been trying to post some clips here and there!
Never been there.. but based on the toppo Dan posted and the background of the video... Long Point?
Nope - part of another great lake - and I know you've been there!
